                  <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Contact your insurance directly for exact coverage details</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
              <strong>Important:</strong> Even with PPO insurance, you'll likely pay a significant portion out-of-pocket. The balance can be covered through financing options or cash discounts.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

